title: 01/08/21 - HOUR 1 - NCAAF, Sean Salisbury
itunes:title: 01/08/21 - HOUR 1 - NCAAF, Sean Salisbury
description:
On today's episode of The Dan Patrick Show, the guys take a dive into National Title game, and how things may play out with the Ohio State. Also the Tennessee Volunteers and Georgia Bulldogs are under investigation for recruiting. Also Sean Salisbury joins to talk about the rumors of Deshaun Watson wanting out of Houston and more.
